                    <locus from="1r" to="124v" facs="003">Fols 1r–124v</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur">Mazmura Dāwit</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                    <note>Introductory Prayer from <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3985Mazmura">Mazmura
                                                  Dǝngǝl</title>:
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነዓ ኅቤየ ዳዊት ንጉሠ እስራኤል።
                    በዓለ መዝሙር ሠናይ ወጥዑመ ቃል።
                    ታለብወኒ ነገረ (ወ)ፍካሬ (ኩሉ) አምሳል።
                    ከመ እወድሳ ለማርያም ድንግል።
                    እንዘ እጸርኅ ወዕብል።</foreign>
                    </note>
                  </msItem>

